					"text" : "Bringing this library to Max today is a great example of how we can extend and redefine the very usage \nof compositional techniques initially designed to work in pure “deferred-time”. This is even more the case for tools such as Chréode, created before PatchWork, when the main interface was Lisp code itself.",
